"We’re dedicated to providing quick\n"
"                                                                and effective solutions to ensure\n"
"                                                                your satisfaction."
msgstr ""
"Vi er dedikerede til at levere hurtige\n"
"                                                                og effektive "
"løsninger for at sikre\n"
"                                                                din "
"tilfredshed."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
